      • updateEventValidation

        public static boolean updateEventValidation(EventDTO eventDTO)
        Validates new information about event which is going to be updated. Fields that represent information about event shouldn't be empty. Event's end date should be after it's start date. Event's start date should be after game coupon's end date. Event should end in 2 days since game coupon's end date. If event has passed we are able to set statuses Closed (result can not be Unknown-4) or Cancelled (result should be Unknown-4). If event has't passed yet we are able to set any statuses except Closed (result - Unknown-4 only).
        Parameters:
        eventDTO - EventDTO object that represents new event.
        Returns:
        true if validation passed successfully. false otherwise.

      • updateGameCouponValidation

        public static boolean updateGameCouponValidation(GameCupounDTO gameDTO)
        Validates new information about game coupon which is going to be updated. Fields that represent information about game coupon shouldn't be empty. Jackpot should be greater then zero or equal to it. Minimum bet amount should be greater then zero. Game coupon's end date should be after it's start date.
        Parameters:
        gameDTO - GameCupounDTO object that represents particular game coupon.
        Returns:
        true if validation passed successfully. false otherwise.
